race.comment: PRETENTIOUS (3) scored by 3.5 lengths last time (19.95) in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Looks the one to beat with even luck. IMPECCABLE (1) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 2.75 lengths at this track in a handy 20.24. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. CALLA NAUGHTY (2) goes very well this course and distance starting 12 times for five wins and three minors. Comes off a (20.17) win last time, scoring by 1.5 lengths in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. TIDDLER BOY (4) is a last start winner and can go on with it.
